%% Startup Sequence (v0.02)
sequenceDiagram
  participant OS as OS
  participant App as Flutter App
  participant Pref as Local Storage
  participant SB as Supabase

  OS->>App: Launch
  App->>App: Render first frame (default theme)
  App->>Pref: Load theme preference (async)
  App->>SB: Restore session (async)
  Pref-->>App: Theme mode
  SB-->>App: Session state
  App->>App: Route to correct home
